General.Name: Bowhead Health
General.Description:
Bowhead is a company with a team of medical doctors, biochemistry and data scientists, software and robotics engineers, designers and wellness coaches.

By using Blockchain, health records can be inter-operable across different platforms, hospital systems and services, while remaining secure and up to date.

Bowhead believes that health data is some of the most valuable data in the world. Bowhead will use anonymized customer health data to add value, while ensuring data is protected using cryptography. Customers gain access to healthcare and may also benefit financially by leasing access to their data in an anonymized manner.

ICO.Description:
Ahoolee is the world’s first search engine dedicated to online shopping worldwide. Ahoolee uses a decentralized platform for open collecting and indexing information from open sources with confirmation of authenticity based on blockchain technology.

Ahoolee will be holding its ICO on August, 2017. There will be a total of 25,000,000 coins available for $0.15 USD each at the offering, with a Cap of 10,000,000 USD. The ICO is expected to end on September 11, 2017, or when the funding cap is reached.
